thing for our own use – but quickly realized – there was enormous pain in this marketplace.  Top-tier freelancers proclaimed: “We need a place to hang our shingle!  Where Clients want high quality, for a fair price.”\r\n<br><br>\r\n<strong>WorkDesq</strong> intends to answer that call.  We understand the pain -- as both Client & Freelancer -- and we are working extra hard to create the best place to obtain freelance work!\r\n</p>";s:14:"home2_html2_bg";s:71:"http://workdesqdev.belfy.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/our-story-bg.jpg";s:17:"home2_html2_color";s:0:"";s:16:"home2_html3_text";s:1696:"<h1 class="page-title1">How it Works</h1>\r\n[grid12]\r\n[one_third first="true"]\r\n[note text="\r\n<strong>Get started</strong> <br><a href=''https://workdesq.wufoo.com/forms/m5pors21jaof6p'' target=''_blank''>HIRE</a> or <a href=''https://workdesq.wufoo.com/forms/zae4c9q0wxjbik/'' target=''_blank''>WORK</a>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<strong>Create job post</strong> <br>Our system helps you create a strong post/profile (10 min)\r\n<br><br>\r\n<strong>Let''s chat</strong> <br>Once Client submits post, you’re prompted to book a 15-min phone chat with us.\r\n" color="#2c9ce6" title="Step 1" button=""][/note]\r\n\r\n[/one_third]\r\n\r\n[one_third]\r\n\r\n[note text="\r\n<strong>Job Proposals</strong> <br>After our chat, WorkDesq vets Freelancers on Client’s behalf, then provides up to 3 proposals (time, budget, etc.)\r\n<br><br>\r\n<strong>Negotiate</strong> <br>WorkDesq helps facilitate negotiations, personally communicating with all parties (Now isn’t that nice!)\r\n<br><br>\r\n<strong>Client awards project</strong> <br>Client & Freelancer/s come to terms\r\n<br><br>\r\n<strong>WorkDesq passes the baton</strong> <br>Client & Freelancer/s now communicate directly throughout the remainder of the project\r\n" color="#313a43" title="Step 2" button=""][/note]\r\n\r\n[/one_third]\r\n\r\n[one_third last="true"]\r\n\r\n[note text="\r\n<strong>We’ll check-in!</strong> <br>To offer help, or to simply say “hello!”\r\n<br><br>\r\n<strong>Complete Project</strong> <br>Client gets final deliverables, Freelancer is fully compensated, WorkDesq deducts 8% from invoice (How’s that for transparency!)\r\n<br><br>\r\n<strong>Repeat!</strong> <br>Visit us again, & tell your friends!\r\n" color="#f47a20" title="Step 3" button=""][/note]\r\n\r\n[/one_third]\r\n\r\n[/grid12]";s:14:"home2_html3_bg";s:0:"";s:17:"home2_html3_color";s:0:"";s:16:"home2_html4_text";s:164:"<h1 class="page-title1">Contact Us</h1>\r\n<p class="page-title2"></p>\r\n \r\n[gravityform id="1" name="Newsletter SignUp" title="false" description="false" ajax="true"]";s:14:"home2_html4_bg";s:0:"";s:17:"home2_html4_color";s:0:"";s:17:"portfolio_grid_no";s:1:"3";s:25:"portfolio_details_outside";s:1:"0";s:24:"portfolio_infinitescroll";s:1:"0";s:14:"portfolio_page";s:1:"0";s:20:"portfolio_item_extra";s:0:"";s:15:"journal_grid_no";s:1:"3";s:23:"journal_details_outside";s:1:"1";s:22:"journal_infinitescroll";s:1:"0";s:13:"blog_sidebar2";s:1:"1";s:14:"sidebar_layout";s:5:"right";s:12:"journal_page";s:1:"0";s:14:"journal_layout";s:5:"right";s:17:"single_post_extra";s:0:"";s:13:"contact_email";s:18:"hello@workdesq.com";s:15:"contact_subject";s:34:"Message received from WorkDesq.com";s:18:"contact_gmap_embed";s:0:"";s:15:"contact_twitter";s:1:"1";s:18:"contact_twitter_id";s:0:"";s:16:"contact_headline";s:10:"Contact Us";s:12:"contact_home";s:0:"";s:16:"contact_location";s:0:"";s:18:"contact_info_email";s:0:"";s:14:"contact_mobile";s:0:"";s:13:"contact_phone";s:0:"";s:11:"contact_fax";s:0:"";s:23:"contact_additional_info";s:14:"Pittsburgh, PA";s:21:"contact_wpcontent_dir";s:10:"wp-content";s:14:"footer_blocks2";a:2:{s:7:"enabled";a:1:{s:7:"placebo";s:7:"placebo";}s:8:"disabled";a:28:{s:7:"placebo";s:7:"placebo";s:8:"facebook";s:8:"Facebook";s:7:"twitter";s:7:"twitter";s:8:"linkedin";s:8:"linkedin";s:7:"youtube";s:7:"youtube";s:6:"envato";s:6:"envato";s:3:"rss";s:3:"rss";s:6:"amazon";s:6:"amazon";s:7:"behance";s:7:"beha